intro:
A boring game like bowling that actually is not boring!
Let’s go to Brazil from Japan!
description:
This is very simple action game.

Brazil is antipodal to Japan. You dig a hole to go to Brazil to Japan!

・You can know the whole world!
The game has many countries as goals.
Let’s try to get all countries and secret places.
